Package: treeExtension
Type: Package
Title: Lightweight Utilities for IQ-TREE Outputs
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Chen", "Yanpeng", email = "yanpengch@qq.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Utilities for working with IQ-TREE outputs and BLAST tabular 
    results. Includes 'make_binary_iqtree()' to convert an unrooted tree into a
    rooted binary tree by splitting the outgroup pendant branch length equally
    (L/2 + L/2), and 'map_blastn_2_iqtree()' to summarize within-node pairwise
    identities (pident) from BLASTN outfmt 6 files on internal nodes.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 3.5)
Imports:
    ggtree,
    ggplot2,
    tidytree,
    treeio,
    readr,
    dplyr,
    tibble
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
